20reinstate%20delisted%20Indian%20apps%20after%20meeting%20Union%20Information%20Technology%20minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20and%20also%20interactions%20with%20the%20startup%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20spirit%20of%20cooperation%2C%20we%20are%20temporarily%20reinstating%20the%20apps%20of%20the%20developers%20with%20appeals%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Google%20maintains%20its%20right%20to%20implement%20and%20enforce%20its%20business%20model%2C%20as%20established%20in%20various%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Google%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fvaishnaw-meets-startup-google-tech-giant-agrees-to-restore-status-quo-124030500976_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Business%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConditional%20Reinstatement%20of%20Apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoogle%2C%20however%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20begin%20%E2%80%98invoicing%E2%80%99%20its%20full%20applicable%20services%20fees%20in%20the%20interim%2C%20but%20was%20extending%20payment%20timelines%20for%20these%20companies%2C%20until%20a%20resolution%20is%20achieved%20in%20courts.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20given%20Indian%20startups%20any%20relief%20in%20their%20plea%20against%20fees%20(11-30%25)%20being%20charged%20by%20Google%20for%20in-app%20purchases%20in%20their%20Play%20Store.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20look%20forward%20to%20a%20collaborative%20effort%20to%20find%20solutions%20that%20respect%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20company%20has%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYesterday%2C%20minister%20Vaishnaw%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20held%20multiple%20discussions%20with%20the%20affected%20startups%20and%20Google.%20%E2%80%9CGoogle%20and%20the%20startup%20community%20have%20met%20us%2C%20and%20we%20have%20had%20a%20constructive%20discussion.%20Google%20has%20agreed%20to%20list%20all%20the%20apps%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnaw%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgoogle-search-modi-govt-now-says-ai-advisory-only-advisory-not-regulatory-framework%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20yesterday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20start-ups%20complaining%20that%20their%20revenue%20stream%20had%20been%20hit%20badly%20after%20not%20being%20available%20for%20download%20on%20the%20Google%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-vs-indian-startups-apps-take-next-big-step-against-alphabet-inc-urge-cci-to-take-action-101709597173811.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0that%20they%20have%20approached%20the%20regulator%2C%20the%20Centre-run%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20again%2C%20to%20get%20all%20apps%20back%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoogle%20first%20delisted%20apps%20by%2010%20Indian%20developers%20for%20not%20complying%20with%20its%20payments%20policy%2C%20about%20sharing%2011-30%25%20service%20fee%20with%20them%20for%20all%20in-app%20purchases%20of%20digital%20goods%20and%20services.%20Companies%20affected%20included%20Info%20Edge%E2%80%99s%20five%20apps%20%E2%80%93%20Naukri.com%2C%20Naukri%20Recruiter%2C%20Naukrigulf%2C%2099acres%20and%20Shiksha.%20By%20Saturday%20afternoon%2C%20three%20of%20these%20apps%20%E2%80%93%20Naukri.com%2C%20Naukrigulf%20and%2099acres%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20re-listed.%20Shaadi.com%20is%20the%20only%20other%20app%20to%20be%20re-listed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle-Government%20Context%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20round%20of%20public%20encounters%20between%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20Google%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20the%20first%20being%20over%20Google%E2%80%99s%20AI%20tool%2C%20Google%20Gemini%E2%80%99s%20answers%20to%20a%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Modi%20a%20fascist%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20answers%20to%20which%20by%20the%20AI%20chatbot%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fai-artificial-intelligence-advisory-rajeev-chandrasekhar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eannoyed%20the%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20junior%20minister%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekhar%20invoked%20IT%20Rules%20when%20he%20complained%20to%20Google%20about%20the%20answer.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20direct%20violations%20of%20Rule%203(1)(b)%20of%20Intermediary%20Rules%20(IT%20rules)%20of%20the%20IT%20act%20and%20violations%20of%20several%20provisions%20of%20the%20Criminal%20code.%20%40GoogleAI%20%40GoogleIndia%20%40GoI_MeitY%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20did%20not%20explain%20how%20a%20statement%20of%20fact%20about%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Che%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20implementing%20policies%20that%20some%20experts%20have%20characterised%20as%20fascist%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20violates%20a%20law.%20Google%20however%2C%20backtracked%20on%20the%20tool%20and%20termed%20other%20responses%20given%20by%20the%20AI%20tool%20raised%20by%20other%20right%20wing%20supporters%20globally%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20unacceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F02%2F27%2F2024%2Fgoogle-ceo-sundar-pichai-calls-ai-tools-responses-completely-unacceptable%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESemafore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20citing%20an%20internal%20memo.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20also%20issued%20a%20controversial%20%E2%80%98advisory%E2%80%99%20for%20AI%20tools%20to%20seek%20