%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Predicted%20XI%20vs%20England%205th%20Test%3A%20Padikkal%20To%20Replace%20Patidar%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20Team%20India%20is%20all%20set%20to%20take%20on%20England%20in%20the%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20of%20the%20five-match%20series%2C%20starting%20March%207%20at%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%2C%20Dharamsala.%20The%20Anthony%20de%20Mello%20Trophy%20has%20already%20been%20clinched%20by%20India%20as%20they%20head%20into%20the%20fifth%20match%20of%20the%20series%20with%20a%203-1%20lead.%20England%20began%20the%20series%20on%20a%20winning%20note%20at%20Hyderabad.%20However%2C%20India%20bounced%20back%20with%20three%20successive%20wins%20to%20hand%20England%20their%20first%20Test%20series%20defeat%20since%20Brendon%20McCullum%20and%20Ben%20Stokes%20took%20charge%20as%20coach%20and%20captain%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeading%20into%20the%20Dharamsala%20Test%2C%20team%20India%20is%20mulling%20over%20the%20possibility%20give%20a%20Test%20cap%20to%20Karnataka's%20Devdutt%20Padikkal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20KL%20Rahul%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%20final%20Test%20and%20Rajat%20Patidar%20has%20failed%20to%20impress%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20it%20seems%20likely%20that%20Padikkal%20will%20get%20the%20nod%20for%20the%20fifth%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20reached%20500%20Test%20wickets%20in%20Rajkot%2C%20becoming%20the%20second-fastest%20to%20the%20milestone%20in%20terms%20of%20Tests%20played%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20play%20his%20100th%20Test%20at%20Dharamsala.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20India's%20predicted%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20fifth%20Test%20against%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Predicted%20Playing%20XI%20against%20England%20in%20the%20Fifth%20Test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20has%20been%20having%20a%20dream%20run%20in%20the%20ongoing%20series%20as%20the%20southpaw%20has%20amassed%20655%20runs%20in%20eight%20innings%20at%20an%20impressive%20average%20of%2093.57.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Jaiswal%20has%20smashed%20two%20hundreds%20and%20just%20as%20many%20fifties%20with%20his%20highest%20score%20being%20214*%20at%20Rajkot.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(c)%20has%20had%20his%20share%20of%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20red-ball%20format%20since%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20However%2C%20the%20batting%20legend%20has%20done%20well%20to%20lead%20an%20inexperienced%20team%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20prominent%20names%20like%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe's%20scored%20297%20runs%20in%20the%20series%20so%20far%20at%20an%20average%20of%2037.12%20and%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20lead%20his%20team%20by%20example%20in%20the%20final%20Test%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Shubman%20Gill%20has%20had%20a%20rollercoaster%20ride%20in%20the%20ongoing%20red-ball%20series.%20After%20failing%20to%20score%20runs%20in%20the%20Hyderabad%20Test%2C%20he%20bounced%20back%20with%20a%20majestic%20hundred%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20at%20Vizag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20has%20accumulated%20342%20runs%20in%20four%20Tests%20at%20a%20decent%20average%20of%2048.85.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%20replaced%20an%20injured%20KL%20Rahul%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20his%20debut%20in%20the%20fifth.%20Padikkal%20has%20done%20well%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20has%20made%20556%20runs%20from%20six%20innings%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Ranji%20Trophy%20for%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%202016%20U19%20World%20Cup%20and%20earned%20his%20debut%20for%20India%20after%20accumulating%20plenty%20of%20runs%20on%20the%20domesti