%20up%20posters%20in%20the%20constituency.%20%26quot%3BTake%20Congress's%20development%20work%20forward%2C%20Rae%20Bareli%20is%20calling%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20ji%2C%20please%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20poster%20read.%20The%20posters%20have%20photographs%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20freedom%20fighter%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Azad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20has%20not%20announced%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202014%20and%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20Congress%20managed%20to%20win%20Rae%20Bareli%20despite%20a%20wave%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20immense%20interest%20surrounding%20the%20BJP's%20pick%20for%20this%20seat%20and%20whether%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20vacating%20the%20seat%20will%20impact%20the%20Congress's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20fielded%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20from%20the%20seat.%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20who%20lost%20to%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20by%20a%20margin%20of%201.60%20lakh%20votes%2C%20has%20said%20whoever%20the%20party%20chooses%20this%20time%20will%20have%20his%20full%20support.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20help%20him%20fight%20elections%20with%20all%20my%20heart%2C%20body%2C%20mind%2C%20and%20wealth.%20It%20is%20my%20resolve%20to%20make%20the%20lotus%20blossom%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%2C%20now%20a%20state%20minister%2C%20recently%20said%20in%20a%20social%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Amethi%2C%20another%20prestige%20seat%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20retained%20Union%20Minister%20and%20sitting%20MP%20Smriti%20Irani%20as%20its%20candidate.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time%20Ms%20Irani%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20Amethi.%20Following%20a%20defeat%20in%20the%202014%20election%2C%20she%20had%20come%20ba