%20Trophy%20provides%20national%20players%20an%20opportunity%20to%20go%20back%20to%20basics%20while%20also%20elevating%20the%20level%20of%20the%20domestic%20tournament.%20The%20BCCI%20recently%20made%20it%20mandatory%20for%20its%20centrally%20contracted%20players%20to%20play%20domestic%20red-ball%20cricket%20if%20they%20aren't%20on%20national%20duty%20or%20in%20the%20NCA.%20The%20BCCI%20excluded%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20from%20its%20central%20contract%20list%20after%20they%20missed%20their%20state%20team's%20respective%20Ranji%20Trophy%20games.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20India%20players%20turn%20up%20for%20their%20domestic%20teams%2C%20it%20raises%20the%20quality%20of%20play%20for%20youngsters%20and%20sometimes%20new%20talent%20is%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20also%20gives%20the%20national%20players%20a%20chance%20to%20sometimes%20rediscover%20the%20basics%2C%26quot%3B%20Tendulkar%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20my%20career%2C%20I%20remained%20passionate%20about%20playing%20for%20Mumbai%20whenever%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity.%20Growing%20up%2C%20we%20had%20almost%207-8%20India%20players%20in%20our%20dressing%20room%2C%20and%20it%20was%20fun%20to%20play%20alongside%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Tendulkar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Ranji%20Trophy%20semi-finals%20have%20been%20riveting!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMumbaiCricAssoc%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MumbaiCricAssoc%3C%2Fa%3E's%20march%20into%20the%20finals%20was%20aided%20by%20a%20brilliant%20batting%20recovery%2C%20while%20the%20other%20semi-final%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance%20going%20into%20the%20last%20day%20-%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20need%2090%2B%20runs%20to%20win%2C%20Vidarbha%20need%204%20wickets.%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20(%40sachin_rt)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fs