s%20birthday%20celebrations%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Army%20initially%20said%20that%20Catherine%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%20Prince%20William%2C%20would%20review%20soldiers%20on%20June%208%20as%20part%20of%20the%20annual%20Trooping%20the%20Colour%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKate%20and%20William's%20Kensington%20Palace%20office%20did%20not%20formally%20confirm%20her%20appearance%20and%20the%20Army%20later%20removed%20a%20reference%20to%20it%20from%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20came%20just%2024%20hours%20after%20Kate%20was%20spotted%20in%20public%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20she%20underwent%20abdominal%20surgery%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20photos%20published%20by%20US%20outlet%20TMZ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army's%20website%20listed%20the%20king%2C%20who%20is%20being%20treated%20for%20cancer%2C%20as%20attending%20the%20main%20military%20parade%20on%20June%2015%2C%20which%20marks%20his%20official%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles%2C%2075%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20held%20an%20in-person%20audience%20with%20finance%20minister%20Jeremy%20Hunt%2C%20who%20delivers%20the%20government's%20budget%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20head%20of%20state%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20blue%20suit%20and%20a%20light%20tie%2C%20was%20photographed%20shaking%20hands%20with%20Hunt%20as%20he%20welcomed%20him%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles%2C%20who%20became%20king%20in%20September%202022%20following%20the%20death%20of%20his%20mother%20Elizabeth%20II%2C%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20an%20unspecified%20cancer%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20princess%20has%20been%20recovering%20mainly%20at%20the%20home%20she%20shares%20with%20William%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children%20in%20Windsor%2C%20west%20of%20London%2C%20since%20leaving%20hospital%20on%20January%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20photos%20published%20by%20TMZ%20showed%20Kate%20wearing%20sunglasses%20while%20being%20driven%20by%20her%20mother%20in%20a%20car.%20The%20celebrity%20news%20site%20said%20the%20images%20were%20taken%20on%20Monday%20near%20Windsor%20Castle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20alight%20with%20conspiracy%20theories%20over%20the%20princess's%20prolonged%20absence%20from%20the%20spotlight.%20Rather%20than%20suppressing%20rumours%2C%20Joe%20Little%2C%20managing%20editor%20of%20Majesty%20Magazine%2C%20said%20the%20photograph%20had%20%26quot%3Bgenerated%20more%20speculation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tricky%20situation%20because%20we're%20all%20entitled%20to%20our%20privacy%20when%20we%20are%20unwell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20you%20are%20a%20member%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20that%20is%20quite%20complicated%20and%20difficult%20to%20maintain%2C%20there%20is%20naturally%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20public%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ERoyal%20shortage%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20illnesses%20of%20Charles%20and%20Catherine%20have%20given%20rise%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20uncertainty%20around%20the%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%20himself%20missed%20events%20to%20look%20after%20his%20family.%20He%20also%20pulled%20out%20of%20a%20recent%20memorial%20service%20for%20his%20late%20godfather%20King%20Constantine%20II%20of%20Greece%20over%20an%20unspecified%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles's%20wife%20Queen%20Camilla%2C%2076%2C%20has%20been%20the%20most%20visible%20senior%20royal%2C%20stepping%20in%20to%20cover%20many%20of%20her%20husband's%20public%20duties%20during%20his%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20now%20on%20a%20break%20until%20March%2011%2C%20when%20she%20is%20expected%20to%20join%20William%20and%20other%20senior%20royals%20at%20the%20annual%20Commonwealth%20Day%20service%20at%20Westminster%20Abbey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20reported%20to%20be%20on%20holiday%20this%20week%2C%20effectively%20meaning%20all%20four%20of%20the%20most%20senior%20royals%20are%20out%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%2C%2041%2C%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20public%20on%20Thursday%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20London%20synagogue%2C%20where%20he%20condemned%20the%20rise%20of%20anti-Semitism%20in%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20attended%20last%20month's%20BAFTA%20film%20awards%20ceremony%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKate's%20last%20public%20appearance%20was%20on%20December%2025%20when%20the%20royals%20attended%20a%20Christmas%20Day%20church%20service%20--%20around%20three%20weeks%20before%20she%20was%20admitted%20to%20hospital%20for%20abdominal%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoyal%20officials%20refused%20to%20say%20what%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20for%20but%20said%20the%20condition%20was%20non-cancerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20spent%20almost%20two%20weeks%20in%20hospital%20and%20Kensington%20Palace%20said%20she%20was%20unlikely%20to%20return%20to%20public%20duties%20until%20after%20Easter%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20princess%2C%20widely%20known%20as%20Kate%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20William%20have%20taken%20on%20more%20royal%20duties%20since%20his%20younger%20brother%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20his%20wife%20Meghan%20left%20for%20the%20United%20States%20in%202020%2C%20and%20the%20king's%20brother%20Prince%20Andrew%20stepped%20back%20because%20of%20his%20friendship%20with%20the%20convicted%20sex%20offender%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709693640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fjqh7ke9o_kate-middleton_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news