if-indians-can-be-proud-singer-chinmayi-sripaada-on-spanish-tourists-gang-rape-5184837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Vaccinated%20Over%20200%20Times%20Against%20Covid-19%2C%20Scientists%20Puzzled%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2062-year-old%20German%20man%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20received%20over%20200%20COVID-19%20vaccines%20has%20become%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20scientific%20study.%20Researchers%20were%20surprised%20by%20the%20reports%20and%20are%20now%20investigating%20the%20man's%20immune%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analysis%2C%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flaninf%2Farticle%2FPIIS1473-3099(24)00134-8%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELancet%20Infectious%20Diseases%20journal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20looks%20at%20the%20effects%20of%20repeated%20vaccinations%20on%20a%20man's%20immunity.%20Even%20after%20allegedly%20receiving%20217%20doses%2C%20the%20vaccines%20appear%20to%20be%20generating%20antibodies%20and%20increasing%20his%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20at%20Friedrich-Alexander-Universitat%20Erlangen-Nurnberg%20and%20hospitals%20in%20Munich%20and%20Vienna%20became%20interested%20in%20the%20case%20after%20hearing%20local%20news%20reports.%20They%20contacted%20the%20man%20and%20invited%20him%20for%20tests%2C%20which%20he%20reportedly%20agreed%20to%20willingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20learned%20about%20his%20case%20via%20newspaper%20articles%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Privatdozent%20Dr%20Kilian%20Schober%20from%20the%20Institute%20of%20Microbiology-Clinical%20Microbiology%2C%20Immunology%2C%20and%20Hygiene%20(director%20Proffessor%20Dr%20Christian%20Bogdan)%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eurekalert.org%2Fnews-releases%2F1036405%5C%22%3Ewritten%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20then%20contacted%20him%20and%20invited%20him%20to%20undergo%20various%20tests%20in%20Erlangen.%20He%20was%20very%20interested%20in%20doing%20so.%26quot%3B%20Schober%20and%20his%20colleagues%20wanted%20to%20know%20what%20consequences%20hypervaccination%20such%20as%20this%20would%20have.%20How%20does%20it%20alter%20the%20immune%20response%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20rule%2C%20vaccinations%20contain%20parts%20of%20the%20pathogen%20or%20a%20type%20of%20construction%20plan%20that%20the%20vaccinated%20person's%20cells%20can%20use%20to%20produce%20these%20pathogenic%20components%20themselves.%20Thanks%20to%20these%20antigens%2C%20the%20immune%20system%20learns%20to%20recognise%20the%20real%20pathogen%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20later%20infection.%20It%20can%20then%20react%20more%20rapidly%20and%20forcibly.%20But%20what%20happens%20if%20the%20body's%20immune%20system%20is%20exposed%20extremely%20often%20to%20a%20specific%20antigen%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20may%20be%20the%20case%20in%20a%20chronic%20infection%20such%20as%20HIV%20or%20Hepatitis%20B%2C%20that%20has%20regular%20flare-ups%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Schober.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20certain%20types%20of%20immune%20cells%2C%20known%20as%20T-cells%2C%20then%20become%20fatigued%2C%20leading%20to%20them%20releasing%20fewer%20pro-inflammatory%20messenger%20substances.%26quot%3B%20This%20and%20other%20effects%20triggered%20by%20the%20cells%20becoming%20used%20to%20the%20antigens%20can%20weaken%20the%20immune%20system.%20The%20immune%20system%20is%20then%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20combat%20the%20pathogen%20so%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlood%20samples%20from%20several%20years%20investigated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20study%2C%20which%20also%20involved%20researchers%20from%20Munich%20and%20Vienna%2C%20does%20not%20deliver%20any%20indication%20that%20this%20is%20the%20case%2C%20however.%20%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20has%20undergone%20various%20blood%20tests%20over%20recent%20years%3B%26quot%3B%20explains%20Schober.%20%26quot%3BHe%20gave%20us%20his%20permission%20to%20assess%20the%20results%20of%20these%20analyses.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20samples%20had%20been%20frozen%2C%20and%20we%20were%20able%20to%20investigate%20these%20ourselves.%20We%20were%20also%20able%20to%20take%20blood%20samples%20ourselves%20when%20the%20man%20received%20a%20further%20vaccination%20during%20the%20study%20at%20his%20own%20insistence.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20use%20these%20samples%20to%20determine%20exactly%20how%20the%20immune%20system%20reacts%20to%20the%20vaccination.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20individual%20has%20a%20large%20number%20of%20T-effector%20cells%20against%20SARS-CoV-2.%20These%20act%20as%20the%20body's%20own%20soldiers%20that%20fight%20against%20the%20virus.%20The%20test%20person%20even%20had%20more%20of%20these%20compared%20to%20the%20control%20group%20of%20people%20who%20have%20received%20three%20vaccinations.%20The%20researchers%20did%20not%20perceive%20any%20fatigue%20in%20these%20effector%20cells%2C%20they%20were%20similarly%20effective%20as%20those%20in%20the%20control%20group%20who%20had%20received%20the%20normal%20number%20of%20vaccinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709692560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2F91ruk77g_covid19-vaccine-generic-bloomberg_625x300_03_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fman-vaccinated-over-200-times-against-covid-19-scientists-puzzled-5184836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Doctors%20at%20Friedrich-Alexander-Universitat%20Erlangen-Nurnberg%20and%20hospitals%20in%20Munich%20and%20Vienna%20became%20interested%20in%20the%20case%20after%20hearing%20local%20news%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fman-vaccinated-over-200-times-against-covid-19-scientists-puzzled-5184836%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscien