0adviser%20cited%20her%20conversation%20with%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20from%20last%20year%20as%20evidence%20of%20her%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20the%20reason%20she%20would%20probably%20never%20run%20for%20office.%20In%20a%20Netflix%20special%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPolitics%20is%20hard.%20And%20the%20people%20who%20get%20into%20it%20...%20you've%20got%20to%20want%20it.%20It's%20got%20to%20be%20in%20your%20soul%2C%20because%20it%20is%20so%20important.%20It%20is%20not%20in%20my%20soul.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20she%20expressed%20deep%20fear%20about%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bhaunts%26quot%3B%20her.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20people%20think%20that%20government-'eh%2C%2C%20does%20it%20really%20even%20do%20anything%3F'%20-%20and%20I'm%20like%2C%20'Oh%20my%20God%2C%20does%20government%20do%20everything%20for%20us%2C%20and%20we%20cannot%20take%20this%20democracy%20for%20granted.'%20And%20I%20worry%20sometimes%20that%20we%20do.%20Those%20are%20the%20things%20that%20keep%20me%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20Democrats%20who%20voted%20in%20the%20Rasmussen%20Reports%20polls%2C%20expressed%20their%20choice%20for%20someone%20other%20than%20Biden%20to%20fight%20the%20US%20Presidential%20elections.%20About%2048%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Democrats%20polled%20said%20they%20approve%20of%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bfinding%20another%20candidate%20to%20replace%20Joe%20Biden%20before%20the%20election%20in%20November%2C%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%2038%20per%20cent%20who%20disapprove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichelle%20Obama%20got%20about%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20votes%20among%20other%20options%20to%20replace%2081-year-old%20Joe%20Biden.%20The%20other%20contenders%20were%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20former%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20California%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20and%20Michigan%20Governor%20Gretchen%20Whitmer.%3