3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68472310.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEngineer%20Of%20Spin%20Bowling%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-England%20Star's%20Humongous%20Praise%20For%20Ashwin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20out%20in%20glowing%20praise%20of%20a%20member%20of%20his%20tribe%20and%20a%20modern-day%20exponent%20of%20spin%2C%20former%20England%20left-arm%20spinner%20Monty%20Panesar%20labelled%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20the%20%26quot%3Bengineer%20of%20spin%20bowling%26quot%3B.%20The%20fifth%20and%20final%20Test%20against%20England%20at%20the%20picturesque%20HPCA%20stadium%20in%20Himachal's%20Dharamshala%20will%20mark%20Ashwin's%20100th%20in%20the%20red-ball%20format.%20The%20match%20will%20see%20India's%20spinning%20ace%20crossing%20another%20major%20career%20milestone%20after%20picking%20up%20his%20500th%20wicket%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20at%20Rajkot.%20In%20a%20career%20spanning%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20tweaker%20has%20bagged%20507%20wickets%20across%2099%20Tests%20at%20a%20staggering%20average%20of%2023.9%20and%20an%20economy%20of%202.79.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20ranked%20globally%20as%20the%20ninth-highest%20wicket-taker%20in%20Tests%20and%20the%20second-highest%20in%20India%20after%20the%20legendary%20Anil%20Kumble%2C%20Ashwin%20brings%20his%20bag%20of%20tricks%20to%20the%20team%2C%20tying%20opposition%20batsmen%20in%20knots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20unique%20carrom%20ball%2C%20which%20he%20delivers%20with%20a%20flick%20of%20his%20fingers%20from%20a%20front-on%20action%2C%20is%20a%20weapon%20in%20his%20bowling%20armoury%20that%20has%20made%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20best%20batters%2C%20including%20former%20England%20captain%20Alistair%20Cook%20and%20retired%20South%20African%20stalwart%20Hashim%20Amla%2C%20look%20clueless%20on%20the%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20myriad%20other%20variations%2C%20including%20the%20slider%2C%20arm%20ball%2C%20and%20topspin%2C%20among%20others%2C%20delivered%20with%20slight%20alterations%20of%20his%20wrist%20position%2C%20have%20kept%20batsmen%20guessing%20through%20the%20years.%20These%20variations%20have%20made%20the%20wily%20operator%20a%20prolific%20wicket-taker%20across%20formats%2C%20especially%20Tests%2C%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20ANI%20over%20the%20phone%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Panesar%20paid%20the%20ultimate%20tribute%20to%20Ashwin%20for%20the%20efforts%20he%20has%20undertaken%20to%20add%20to%20his%20repertoire%20and%20reinvent%20himself%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20has%20been%20absolutely%20brilliant.%20The%20first%20I%20came%20across%20him%20was%20during%20a%20Test%20series%20in%20India%20(2012).%20Role-wise%2C%20he%20has%20been%20there%20working%20out%20angles%20and%20engineering%20his%20way%20to%20dismissals.%20I%20think%20he%20is%20brilliant%20at%20how%20he%20changed%20the%20revolutions%20on%20the%20ball%20and%20enriched%20the%20art%20of%20spin%20bowling.%20It%20is%20all%20about%20angles%2C%20mathematics%20and%20data.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20he%20is%20the%20engineer%20of%20spin%20bowling%2C%26quot%3B%20Panesar%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20his%20debut%20against%20England%20in%202012%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20enjoyed%20massive%20success%20while%20delivering%20many%20wins%20to%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2021%20Tests%20against%20England%2C%20he%20has%20claimed%20105%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2028.88%2C%20with%2012%2F167%20being%20his%20best%20effort%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20five-match%20series%2C%20the%20veteran%20spinner%20has%20claimed%2017%20wickets%20in%20four%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2030.41.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20look%20to%20add%20more%20to%20his%20tally%20and%20go%20past%20lanky%20English%20spinner%20Tom%20Hartley%2C%20who%20has%2020%20wickets%20to%20his%20name%20in%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20currently%20hold%20an%20unassailable%203-1%20lead%20in%20th