ocused%20on%20the%20various%20visions%20for%20the%20role%20it%20will%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E'Huge%20risk'%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20reflect%20on%20%26quot%3Bthe%20duality%20of%20the%20technology%26quot%3B%2C%20Ozge%20Aydogan%20of%20the%20United%20Nations-run%20SDG%20Lab%20told%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20an%20asset%20for%20the%20future%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20a%20huge%20risk%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECERN%20chief%20Fabiola%20Gianotti%20meanwhile%20said%20the%20landmark%20nuclear%20research%20lab%20was%20the%20perfect%20place%20for%20the%20centre%2C%20which%20would%20benefit%20from%20its%20long%20experience%20in%20%26quot%3Bemploying%20scientific%20and%20technological%20progress%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computing%20combines%20advances%20in%20scientific%20understanding%20of%20the%20subatomic%20world%20with%20leaps%20in%20information%20theory%20to%20solve%20mathematical%20problems%20that%20are%20impossible%20for%20today's%20conventional%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20traditional%20computers%20process%20information%20in%20bits%20that%20can%20be%20represented%20by%200%20or%201%2C%20quantum%20computers%20use%20qubits%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20combination%20of%20both%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20solve%20more%20complex%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20commercial%20quantum%20computers%20are%20still%20believed%20to%20be%20up%20to%20a%20decade%20away%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20be%20fully%20developed%20before%20around%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrabeck-Latmathe%2C%20the%20former%20longtime%20head%20of%20Swiss%20food%20giant%20Nestle%2C%20said%20it%20was%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20such%20a%20powerful%20technology%20was%20governed%20in%20an%20open%20and%20transparent%20way%20and%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20be%20controlled%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20giant%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20quantum%20computing%20still%20under%20development%2C%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Btime%20to%20think%20about%20what's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20new%20technologies%20...%20the%20ethical%20considerations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20will%20seek%20out%20applications%20of%20the%20technology%20that%20can%20move%20the%20world%20closer%20to%20implementing%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computing%20simulations%20and%20calculations%20might%20for%20instance%20help%20determine%20how%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20dioxide%20in%20the%20atmosphere%20to%20help%20rein%20in%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20also%20potentially%20predict%20patterns%20of%20antibiotic%20resistance%2C%20and%20identify%20new%2C%20more%20effective%20chemical%20compounds%20for%20battling%20deadly%20bacteria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20search%20for%20the%20best%20applications%20of%20the%20technology%2C%20GESDA%20has%20joined%20forces%20with%20Google%20and%20non-profit%20tech%20group%20XPrize%20and%20launched%20a%20competition%20Tuesday%20calling%20for%20researchers%20everywhere%20to%20submit%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-year%20competition%20will%20reward%20the%20teams%20submitting%20the%20best%20projects%2C%20with%20%245%20million%20in%20prizes%20at%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709689860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fihh3b9ko_quantum-computers_625x300_06_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhas-potential-to-change-almost-everything-scientists-to-channel-quantum-power-5184693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20will%20work%20to%20channel%20the%20huge%20eme