%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108250589%2Cimgsize-123188.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fpro-farm-social-media-accounts-suspended-in-jalandhar%2Farticleshow%2F108250590.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20accounts%2C%20including%20those%20of%20independent%20journalists%20and%20pro-farm%20handles%2C%20have%20been%20blocked%20in%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20blocking.%20X's%20global%20government%20affairs%20expressed%20disagreement%20with%20the%20actions%2C%20while%20Punjab-based%20journalists%20have%20faced%20similar%20heat%20in%20the%20past.%20Independent%20journalists%20%40gurshamshir%2C%20%40praveenpscs%2C%20and%20%40gravitgarg15%2C%20whose%20accounts%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%2C%20have%20been%20reporting%20regularly%20on%20the%20farm%20protests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22IP%20SINGH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchandigarh%2Fpro-farm-social-media-accounts-suspended-in-jalandhar%2Farticleshow%2F108250590.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20To%20Promise%20%26quot%3BRight%20To%20Employment%26quot%3B%20To%20Youth%20In%20Poll%20Manifesto%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeeking%20to%20woo%20the%20country's%20youth%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20offer%20them%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20to%20employment%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20its%20poll%20promise%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20besides%20mulling%20stringent%20punishment%20to%20those%20responsible%20for%20paper%20leaks%20in%20examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20top%20leadership%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20an%20announcement%20on%20the%20'right%20to%20employment'%20during%20a%20public%20rally%20at%20Badanawar%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20both%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20former%20party%20chief%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20party%20sources%20said%20the%20promises%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20finalised%20soon%2C%20once%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20approves%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20that%20such%20a%20scheme%20to%20give%20'right%20to%20employment'%20will%20be%20given%20to%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20country%20and%20some%20allowance%20may%20also%20be%20offered%20to%20the%20youth%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20developed%20countries%20do%20not%20offer%20their%20youth%20such%20a%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20would%20also%20provide%20for%20a%20stringent%20law%20and%20punishment%20against%20those%20responsible%20for%20paper%20leaks%20in%20the%20country%20and%20will%20suggest%20measures%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20government%20recruitments%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20come%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20during%20the%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%20has%20focussed%20on%20the%20plight%20of%20lakhs%20of%20students%20suffering%20due%20to%20frequent%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cancellation%20of%20exams%20thereafter%20in%20some%20cases%20like%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20thrust%20of%20the%20manifesto%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20on%20the%205-nyay%20(five%20pillars%20of%20justice)%20promised%20by%20the%20Congress%20during%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20'Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra'%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20would%20also%20focus%20on%20giving%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20minimum%20support%20price%20and%20promising%20a%20caste-based%20census%20in%20the%20country%20for%20filling%20up%20the%20government%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20likely%20to%20give%20a%20thrust%20to%20some%20welfare%20measures%20like%20providing%20financial%20assistance%20to%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20ensuring%20that%20they%20get%20justice%20and%20be%20part%20of%20the%20state%20welfare%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20Congress%20promises%20made%20to%20the%20people%20helped%20the%20party%20get%20into%20power%20in%20states%20like%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20recently.%20The%20Congress%20manifesto%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20former%20union%20minister%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20met%20here%20to%20give%20a%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20manifesto%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20at%20a%20five-hour%20meeting%20last%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20members%20of%20the%20party's%20manifesto%20committee%20were%20present%20during%20the%20meeting%20at%20the%20AICC%20headquarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChidambaram%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20given%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20draft%20manifesto%20which%20will%20become%20the%20party%20document%20once%20the%20CWC%20approves%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20wound%20up%20internal%20deliberations%20for%20giving%20final%20shape%20to%20the%20party%20manifesto%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20include%20some%20innovative%20measures%20like%20an%20apprenticeship%20scheme%20for%20the%20youth%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20completed%20our%20draft%20manifesto.%20It's%20a%20draft.%20It%20will%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20working%20committee.%20It%20is%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20which%20finalises%20the%20manifesto%20and%20then%20it%20becomes%20a%20Congress%20party%20document.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20have%20completed%20the%20work%20on%20the%20draft%20manifesto%2C%26quot%3B%20Chidambaram%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20to%20be%20able%20to%20present%20it%20to%20the%20Congress%20president%20along%20with%20members%20available%20in%20Delhi%20sometime%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3