n%20the%20need%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Can%20open%20space%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmeaningful%20participation%20in%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20particularly%20important%20in%20a%20pre-electoral%20context%20to%20ensure%20an%20open%20space%20that%20respects%20the%20meaningful%20participation%20of%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Turk%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20he%20welcomed%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20landmark%20electoral%20bonds%20judgment%20in%20which%20the%20scheme%20was%20declared%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20and%20violative%20of%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1218090%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Article%2019(1)(a)%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20welcome%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20last%20month%20on%20campaign%20finance%20schemes%2C%20upholding%20the%20right%20to%20information%20and%20transparency%2C%E2%80%9D%20Turk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsbi-electoral-bonds-ridiculous-deepak-gupta-karan-thapar%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Believe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20Explanation%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds%3B%20It%E2%80%99s%20Absolutely%20Ridiculous%E2%80%99%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20comments%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20UN%20in%20Geneva%2C%20ambassador%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20asserted%20that%20the%20high%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20observations%20were%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20his%20%5BTurk%E2%80%99s%5D%20concerns%20in%20this%20regard%20are%20unwarranted%20and%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20any%20democracy%2C%20argumentation%20is%20natural.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20those%20in%20positions%20of%20authority%20do%20not%20allow%20thei