%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20hereby%20relieve%20myself%20from%20all%20roles%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20party.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FWgjmfaCZiS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FWgjmfaCZiS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Arjun%20Modhwadia%20(%40arjunmodhwadia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farjunmodhwadia%2Fstatus%2F1764659609883553989%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%204%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrabhu%20Ram%20is%20not%20just%20Pujaniya%20to%20Hindus%2C%20but%20he%20is%20the%20Aastha%20of%20Bharat.%20By%20declining%20the%20invitation%20to%20witness%20the%20pran%20pratishtha%20mahotsav%20have%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20Congress%20as%20a%20party%20failed%20to%20assess%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20that%20since%20his%20dissent%20he%20had%20met%20scores%20of%20people%20who%20were%20%E2%80%9Coffended%20by%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20party%20insulted%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%9D%20by%20boycotting%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20further%20distract%20and%20humiliate%20this%20pious%20occasion%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20attempted%20to%20create%20ruckus%20in%20Assam%20which%20further%20angered%20our%20party%20cadres%20and%20citizens%20of%20Bharat%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20then%20on%20the%20Assam%20leg%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-rahul-gandhi-stages-sit-in-after-being-stopped-from-visiting-assam-shrine%5C%22%3Estopped%20from%20visiting%20the%20Batadrava%20Than%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%2015th-century%20Vaishnavite%20religious%20leader%2C%20Srimanta%20Sankardev.%20Subsequently%2C%20Gandhi%C2%A0%20sat%C2%A0%20down%20on%20the%20road%20along%20with%20other%20Congress%20supporters%20who%20sang%20%E2%80%98Raghupati%20Raghav%20Raja%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20and%20above%20since%20(the)%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20helpless%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20people%20my%20district%20Porbandar%20and%20the%20state%20of%20Gujarat%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modhwadia%20said%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20the%20BJP%20comes%20days%20before%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20enters%20the%20state%20on%20March%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20had%20been%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%20over%20four%20decades%20and%20had%20served%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20along%20with%20being%20state%20unit%20chief.%20In%20the%202022%20Gujarat%20assembly%20elections%2C%20he%20defeated%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Babu%20Bokhiria%20in%20Porbandar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Modhwadia%20had%20lent%20his%20support%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgujarat%2Fgujarat-assembly-passes-resolution-hailing-pm-for-ram-temple-event-congress-aap-support-it-2880579%5C%22%3Eunanimous%20resolution%20%3C%2Fa%3Epassed%20in%20the%20Gujarat%20Assembly%20lauding%20Modi%20for%20the%20successful%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20Speaking%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20Modhwadia%20said%20that%20it%20was%20former%20prime%20minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20who%20had%20allowed%20the%20foundation%20stone%20laying%20ceremony%20at%20the%20site%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20however%2C%20Modhwadia%20had%20been%20a%20staunch%20critic%20of%20Modi%2C%20and%20had%20also%20drawn%20the%20ire%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20reprimanded%20Modhwadia%20for%20referring%20to%20Modi%20as%20a%20monkey%20who%20had%20challenged%20the%20lion%20(Manmohan%20Singh)%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgujarat-assembly-elections%2Fec-reprimands-modhwadia-for-his-remarks-against-narendra-modi%2Farticleshow%2F17595975.cms%5C%22%3Ereport%20in%3Cem%3E%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Modhwadia%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2056-inch%20chest%20and%20said%20only%20%E2%80%9Cdonkeys%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2056%20inches%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fit%20person%20has%20a%20chest%20of%2036%20inches%2C%20a%20body-builder%20can%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2042%2C%20it%20is%20only%20donkeys%20who%20have%20a%20chest%20of%2056%20inches%2C%20and%20bulls%20have%20a%20chest%20of%20100%20inches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2019%2FApr%2F09%2Fonly-donkeys-can-have-56-inch-chest-gujarat-congress-leader-arjun-modhwadia-1962332.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModhwadia%20had%20also%20questioned%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20air%20travels%20during%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20was%20Gujarat%20CM%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20travelled%20by%20air%2056%20times%20on%20government%20expense%20before%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Now%2C%20BJP%20should%20repay%20that%20money%20to%20the%20government%20treasury%20and%20Modi%20should%20explain%20such%20serious%20allegations%20about%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modhwadia%20was%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmodi-should-give-explanation-about-his-air-travels-arjun-modhwadia%2Farticleshow%2F39898026.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709647172000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05175110%2FUntitled-design-30.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-gujarat-congress-chief-arjun-modhwadia-joins-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20staunch%20critic%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Modhwadia%20quit%20the%20Congress%20on%20Monday%20and%20said%20that%20the%20party%20had%20failed%20to%20assess%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20with%20its%20decision%20to%20decline%20the%20invitation%20to%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fformer-gujarat-congress-chief-arjun-modhwadia-joins-bjp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Widowhood%2C%20Continuing%20Stigma%2C%20and%20an%20Education%20Rooted%20in%20Reality%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01090729%2F4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Mhatre%20has%20worked%20with%20us%20in%20our%20wadi%20in%20Alibag%20since%201993.%20He%20came%20to%20us%20as%20a%20raw%20twenty-four-year-old%20working%20for%20daily%20wages%20in%20a%20local%20Kirana%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20former%20Navy%20Chief%20relocated%20to%20this%20village%20after%20his%20retirement%20in%201993%20and%20faced%20the%20formidable%20task%20of%20caring%20for%20the%208%20acres%20of%20banjar%20land%20he%20was%20given%20for%20his%20acts%20of%20gallantry%20in%201971%20%E2%80%93%20we%20asked%20for%20someone%20to%20live%20and%20work%20with%20us!!%20Someone%20reliable%2C%20honest%20and%20willing%20to%20learn.%20A%20friend%20who%20knew%20his%20brother%20working%20in%20the%20Collectors%20office%20%E2%80%93%20recommended%20him%20and%20that%20is%20how%20Rajendra%2C%20whom%20we%20fondly%20called%20Harry%2C%20(cos%20he%20resembled%20Harry%20Kumar%20in%20the%20Raj%20Quartet!)%20came%20to%20Ramu%20Farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Mhatre%20and%20Ramu%20Ramdas%20together%20learned%20about%20soils%2C%20trees%2C%20borewells%2C%20and%20greening%20the%20earth.%20I%20was%20busy%20for%20the%20first%20few%20years%20globe%20trotting%20in%20assignments%20with%20my%20then%20work%20concerns.%20Harry%20taught%20us%20%E2%80%98city%20slicks%E2%80%99%20how%20to%20handle%20reptiles%20and%20scorpions%20and%20other%20creatures%20without%20fear%20%E2%80%93%20and%20gradually%20grew%20on%20the%20job%20to%20be%20the%20Man%20Friday%20and%20a%20Jack%20of%20All%20Trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20moved%20to%20Bhaimala%2C%20there%20were%20five%20trees%2C%20two%20species%20of%20birds%20%E2%80%93%20the%20crow%20and%20the%20sparrow%20%E2%80%93%20and%20no%20known%20water%20source.%20Today%20there%20are%20over%202000%20trees%2C%20plants%20and%20shrubs%20and%20the%20bird%20life%20bountiful.%20At%20last%20count%20a%20friend%20identified%20about%2045%20varieties.%20We%20were%20fortunate%20to%20strike%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20advanced%20lung%20cancer%20in%20October%202023.%20Around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20Ramu%20Ramdas%20had%20his%20encounter%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98sudden%20death%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20pacemaker.%20The%20disease%20spread%20rapidly%20and%20metastasised%20to%20the%20bone.%20He%20was%20in%20unbearable%20pain.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20find%20him%20a%20home%20and%20a%20bed%20at%20the%20CIPLA%20Palliative%20Care%20Centre%20in%20Pune%20and%20he%20spent%20the%20last%20month%20of%20his%20life%20relatively%20free%20from%20pain%20and%20in%20a%20calm%20and%20caring%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Rajendra%20passed%20away%20on%20Sunday%2C%20February%2018%2C%202024%2C%20I%20have%20been%20restless%20and%20troubled%20%E2%80%93%20let%20me%20explain%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFacing%20our%20realities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cu%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20how%20tough%20it%20would%20be%20for%20a%20strong%2C%20proud%20woman%20like%20Bharathi%20to%20undergo%20the%20customary%20rites%20and%20rituals%20that%20accompany%20losing%20a%20husband%20in%20a%20traditional%20%E2%80%98Hindu%E2%80%99%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20the%20social%20or%20indeed%20economic%20status%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20these%20fault%20lines%20flow%20seamlessly%20across%20most%20divides%20%E2%80%93%20more%20or%20less%20designed%20to%20assault%20the%20hapless%20woman%20who%20has%20to%20not%20only%20face%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20loved%20one%2C%20but%20then%20has%20to%20undergo%20the%20cruelest%20rituals%20%E2%80%93%20of%20being%20stripped%20of%20all%20those%20%E2%80%98auspicious%E2%80%99%20trappings%20of%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98sumangali%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20one%20who%20is%20a%20married%20woman%20with%20her%20husband%20alive%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethe%20%E2%80%98Bindi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20%E2%80%98bottu%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20sacred%20dot%20on%20the%20forehead%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20%E2%80%98mangal%20sutra%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20or%20thali%20round%20her%20neck%20%E2%80%93%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20%E2%80%98nath%E2%80%99%20or%20nose%20ring%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20earrings%20too%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20bangles%20%E2%80%93%20green%20glass%20here%20in%20Maharashtra%20%E2%80%93%20maybe%20other%20colours%20elsewhere%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20toe%20rings%20%E2%80%93%20and%20anklets%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%20veni%20or%20gajra%20%E2%80%93%20jasmine%20flowers%20in%20her%20hair%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201967%2C%20still%20a%20relatively%20young%20wife%2C%20I%20stood%20by%20numbly%20while%20my%20beloved%20sister-in-law%2C%20Valli%2C%20had%20to%20undergo%20the%20cruel%20and%20insensitive%20rites%20of%20passage%20when%20her%20husband%20Col%20George%20Narayan%20died%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20his%20career.%20I%20remember%20watching%20helplessly%20as%20various%20unknown%20older%20women%20relatives%20got%20to%20work%20on%20relentlessly%20removing%20all%20of%20the%20above%20%E2%80%93%20and%20finally%20taking%20a%20pair%20of%20scissors%20to%20cut%20off%20her%20lovely%20tresses%20%E2%80%93%20at%20our%20home%20in%20J%20Block%2C%20Naval%20Officers%20Flats%2C%20Colaba.%20I%20have%20been%20haunted%20by%20my%20own%20sense%20of%20paralysis%20and%20inability%20to%20stop%20the%20horrific%20rituals%2C%20over%20half%20a%20century%20ago.%20And%20sometimes%20it%20seems%20little%20has%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22M20%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07194357%2FIMG_2649-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671913%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20on%20several%20occasions%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20way%20widows%20are%20insulted%2C%20isolated%20and%20deliberately%20kept%20away%20from%20participating%20in%20weddings%20and%20other%20ceremonies%2C%20since%20they%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%98inauspicious%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%A6.And%20it%20was%20only%20at%20Sagari%20and%20Madhoo%E2%80%99s%20wedding%20at%20Navy%20House%20in%201992%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20make%20amends%20in%20our%20own%20small%20way%2C%20by%20inviting%20our%20close%20and%20beloved%20women%20%5Bwidows!%5D%20of%20the%20family%2C%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20welcoming%20aarti%20which%20would%20otherwise%20have%20been%20only%20done%20by%20Sumangalis!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20I%20watched%20how%20Manasi%2C%20our%20feisty%20executive%20assistant%2C%20refused%20to%20allow%20others%20to%20touch%20her%20after%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20Anand%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20her%20grief%20and%20loss%20%E2%80%93%20but%20still%20had%20to%20bow%20to%20some%20of%20the%20rituals%20which%20were%20impossible%20to%20avoid.%20Rajendra%2C%20who%20accompanied%20me%20to%20Manasi%E2%80%99s%20home%2C%20was%20himself%20quite%20shaken%20and%20disturbed%20by%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time%20it%20is%20women%20who%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20actual%20execution%20of%20these%20heartless%20rituals.%20Except%20in%20some%20villages%20where%20it%20is%20apparently%20a%20man%20who%20is%20called%20in%20to%20actually%20smash%20the%20bangles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20since%20it%20was%20impossible%20for%20me%20to%20actually%20get%20there%20for%20the%20funeral%20%E2%80%93%20I%20called%20and%20spoke%20to%20Bharati%20while%20still%20at%20the%20Pune%20Palliative%20care%20home%20%E2%80%93%20imploring%20her%20not%20to%20allow%20these%20cruel%20rituals.%20And%20to%20tell%20them%20that%20this%20was%20a%20special%20plea%20from%20the%20ninety-year-old%20Admiral.%20Her%20answer%20still%20rings%20in%20my%20ears%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CBai%20if%20you%20were%20there%2C%20maybe%20they%20will%20listen.%20But%20who%20will%20listen%20to%20me%3F%20And%20they%20will%20certainly%20not%20listen%20to%20my%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20is%20the%20background%20to%20what%20happened%20on%20February%2029%20at%20the%2012th-day%20ceremonials%20and%20feeding%20of%20the%20crows%20and%20the%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20deceased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2028%2C%20I%20flew%20to%20Pune%20from%20my%20current%20location%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20spent%20two%20wonderful%20hours%20walking%20around%20the%20Palliative%20Care%20Centre%20%E2%80%93%20visiting%20the%20space%20which%20had%20been%20home%20to%20Rajendra%20and%20Bharathi%20for%20the%20last%20month%20of%20his%20life.%20Dr%20Jyoti%20Gadre%2C%20the%20non-assuming%20and%20impressive%20woman%20who%20had%20been%20my%20link%20person%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20walked%20us%20around%2C%20introduced%20us%20to%20the%20various%20persons%20who%20had%20helped%20to%20make%20his%20last%20days%20comfortable%2C%20relatively%20pain-free%20and%20filled%20with%20love%20and%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20ward%20was%20named%20for%20a%20flower.%20Rajendra%20had%20been%20housed%20in%20Gulab%20ward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20decided%20to%20carry%20a%20bouquet%20of%20red%20roses%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20personal%20tribute%20to%20a%20man%20who%20would%20faithfully%20prepare%20a%20small%20%E2%80%98guccha%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98bunch%E2%80%99%20of%20flowers%20and%20leaves%20%E2%80%93%20to%20present%20us%20on%20our%20birthdays%20and%20anniversaries%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20impulse%2C%20I%20also%20carried%20in%20my%20handbag%20%E2%80%93%20a%20packet%20of%20maroon%20%E2%80%98bindis%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20necklace%20of%20garnets%20and%20one%20green%20bangle%20%E2%80%93%20but%20with%20no%20clear%20idea%20beyond%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20into%20the%20hall%20of%20the%20home%20that%20Rajendra%20had%20taken%20great%20pains%20and%20pride%20to%20complete%20in%20his%20village.%20The%20room%20was%20packed%20with%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%2C%20squatting%20silently.%20And%20a%20table%20with%20a%20large%20photograph%20of%20Rajendra%20where%20the%20offerings%20of%20gaindas%20%5Bmarigolds%5D%20and%20mithais%20were%20piled.%20I%20made%20my%20way%20through%20the%20crowd%20and%20sat%20down%20on%20the%20floor%20next%20to%20Bharati%20%E2%80%93%20and%20just%20held%20her%20as%20she%20and%20I%20sobbed%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20suddenly%20I%20found%20my%20voice%20%E2%80%93%20and%20purpose%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20broken%20Marathi%20and%20Hindi%2C%20I%20asked%20the%20women%20if%20I%20could%20say%20a%20few%20words.%20I%20explained%20to%20them%20about%20the%20red%20roses%20and%20the%20Gulab%20room%20at%20the%20CIPLA%20home%20%E2%80%93%20and%20also%20how%20it%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20floral%20gucchas%20that%20Rajendra%20would%20lovingly%20prepare%20for%20us%20over%20the%20years.%20And%20that%20for%2030%20years%20it%20was%20with%20us%20that%20they%20had%20spent%20the%20longest%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20then%20shared%20the%20message%20from%20Ramdas%20%E2%80%98Saheb%E2%80%99%20sitting%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20unable%20to%20travel%20%E2%80%93%20deeply%20affected%20by%20Rajendra%E2%80%99s%20passing%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20are%20like%20our%20own%20children%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20her%20to%20go%20through%20these%20cruel%20ceremonies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20taking%20a%20deep%20and%20slightly%20nervous%20breath%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20eye%20contact%20with%20as%20many%20as%20possible%2C%20I%20asked%20what%20they%20thought%20about%20these%20cruel%20rituals%20that%20widows%20are%20made%20to%20follow.%20Was%20it%20God%20who%20made%20these%20rules%3F%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CNO%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20there%20was%20a%20collective%20shake%20of%20their%20heads.%20Then%20why%20should%20we%20continue%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20one%20hand%20went%20up%20%E2%80%93%20a%20courageous%20voice%20of%20a%20woman%20who%20had%20been%20widowed%20during%20Covid%2C%20a%20sister-in-law%20of%20Rajendra.%20Through%20her%20tears%2C%20she%20spoke%20of%20the%20indignity%20and%20suffering%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through%2C%20which%20continues%20today.%20She%20was%20emphatic%20that%20no%20one%20should%20ever%20go%20through%20something%20similar.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20silent%20ripple%20running%20through%20the%20room%20%E2%80%93%20empathy%2C%20solidarity%2C%20a%20set%20of%20collective%20doubts%20as%20to%20why%20we%20were%20allowing%20this%20to%20happen.%20But%20also%20fear%20about%20what%20will%20people%20say%20if%20we%20go%20against%20the%20tide.%20It%20was%20important%20to%20let%20some%20time%20pass%2C%20for%20emotions%20to%20be%20processed%2C%20for%20silent%20tears%20to%20be%20dried%20with%20sari%20%E2%80%98Pallus%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20time%20to%20take%20the%20next%20step.%20%C2%A0I%20took%20out%20my%20little%20bag%20%E2%80%93%20told%20them%20what%20I%20was%20planning%20to%20do%20%E2%80%93%20and%20asked%20for%20their%20support%20and%20cooperation.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20asked%20Bharati%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20Nidhi%2C%20if%20she%20would%20do%20the%20needful.%20But%20I%20guess%20Nidhi%20knew%20intuitively%20that%20the%20only%20way%20it%20might%20work%20is%20if%20a%20senior%20citizen%20like%20me%2C%20and%20with%20the%20advantage%20of%20being%20outside%20the%20community%2C%20would%20take%20the%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20asked%20them%20if%20I%20could%20go%20ahead%20%E2%80%93%20and%20there%20was%20a%20silent%20imperceptible%20collective%20signal%20to%20say%20yes%20I%20could.%20Then%20I%20asked%20Bharati%20for%20her%20permission%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20she%20was%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20gently%20put%20the%20Bindi%20on%20to%20Bharati%E2%80%99s%20forehead.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThen%20I%20put%20the%20necklace%20on%20over%20her%20neck.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAnd%20finally%20slipped%20the%20bangle%20on%20her%20hand.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHer%20eyes%20were%20moist%20but%20her%20gaze%20was%20firm%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20could%20feel%20all%20the%20eyes%20on%20me%20%E2%80%93%20as%20I%20held%20her%20after%20it%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20vigorous%20nodding%20of%20heads%20when%20I%20suggested%20that%20unless%20women%20spoke%20up%2C%20none%20of%20these%20cruel%20customs%20would%20change.%20Men%20would%20not%20take%20this%20initiative%20because%20they%20were%20not%20affected.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20also%20asked%20each%20one%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20community%20or%20family%20and%20discuss%20what%20we%20had%20just%20done%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20taken%20an%20important%20step%20to%20ensure%20dignity%20for%20ourselves%20and%20our%20sisters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20now%20it%20was%20time%20for%20all%20those%20gathered%20to%20go%20outside%20to%20bless%20the%20offerings%20of%20all%20his%20favourite%20dishes%20which%20were%20put%20on%20to%20a%20banana%20leaf%20and%20kept%20out%20on%20a%20stool%20for%20the%20crows%20to%20come%20and%20eat.%20We%20believe%20that%20the%20ancestors%20come%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20crows.%20And%20after%20the%20menfolk%20went%20round%20first%2C%20we%20accompanied%20Bharati%20%E2%80%93%20who%20walked%20out%20quite%20un%20self-consciously%2C%20did%20what%20had%20to%20be%20done%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20room.%20We%20exchanged%20glances%2C%20shared%20a%20smile%20%E2%80%93%20an%20unspoken%20communion%20%E2%80%93%20a%20signal%20that%20today%20we%20had%20perhaps%20made%20a%20new%20beginning%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20small%20step%2C%20for%20one%20woman%2C%20in%20one%20village.%20But%20it%20begins%20with%20one%20small%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20we%20continue%20our%20struggles%20for%20all%20the%20big%20battles%20ahead%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20these%20small%20victories%20which%20are%20so%20important%E2%80%A6%20So%20maybe%20this%20will%20become%20the%20first%20topic%20and%20lesson%20one%20in%20our%20Asli%20Taleem%20syllabus%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20little%20group%20of%20village-level%20educators%20had%20chosen%20this%20name%20over%20a%20year%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20after%20having%20worked%20for%20a%20decade%20on%20teaching%20the%20three%20Rs%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20school%20dropouts%20back%20into%20school%20through%20a%20country%20wide%20NGO%20led%20initiative.%20They%20were%20dissatisfied%20with%20just%20formal%20literacy%20and%20numeracy%20and%20felt%20we%20needed%20to%20go%20into%20raising%20and%20addressing%20deeper%20issues%20concerning%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20citizenship%20questions.%20The%20post%20Covid%20revival%20of%20village%20level%20interventions%20has%20generated%20many%20new%20exciting%20possibilities%20in%20our%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20for%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20sleep%20peacefully%20knowing%20this%20day%20we%20might%20have%20ignited%20a%20whole%20different%20set%20of%20ideas%20and%20actions%20%E2%80%93%20connecting%20the%20important%20little%20dots%20to%20begin%20many%20small%20silent%20revolutions%E2%80%A6%20But%20I%20could%20not%20stop%20humming%20the%20words%20of%20our%20old%20and%20well-worn%20songs%20from%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20movement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERaasta%20hai%20Lamba%20Behan%20%E2%80%93%20Manzil%20hai%20dur%3C%2Fem%3E%20(it%E2%80%99s%20a%20long%20road%20ahead%20sisters%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20still%20far%20away)%E2%80%9D.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ETu%20khud%20ko%20badal%2C%20tu%20khud%20ko%20badal%20%E2%80%93%20tab%20hi%20to%20zamaana%20badalega%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%A6.%20(The%20change%20must%20begin%20with%20each%20one%20of%20us%20%E2%80%93%20then%20only%20will%20the%20times%20change)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELalita%20Ramdas%20is%20associated%20with%20LARA%20%E2%80%93%20Ramu%20Farm%2C%20Bhaimala%20Gaon%2C%20Alibag%2C%20Raigad%20District%2C%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709646286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F01090729%2F4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwidowhood-continuing-stigma-and-an-education-rooted-in-reality%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20small%20step%20for%20one%20woman%20in%20one%20village%20where%20it%20all%20begins.%20It%20is%20time%20we%20make%20relevant%20social%2C%20cultural%20and%20citizenship%20issues%20part%20of%20our%20education%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwidowhood-continuing-stigma-and-an-