eral%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficial%20voter%20participation%20in%20the%20election%20was%20barely%2040%25%20(though%20the%20true%20figure%20is%20believed%20to%20me%20much%20lower).%20The%20US%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fus-says-bangladesh-elections-were-not-free-fair-2024-01-08%2F%5C%22%3Eofficially%20criticised%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20violation%20of%20democratic%20rights%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%20approvingly%20maintained%20a%20stoic%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20have%20successfully%20experimented%20with%20another%20gambit%3A%20blocking%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20already%20meagre%20sources%20of%20election%20funding.%20This%20was%20done%20by%20way%20of%20arrests%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fhigher-cash-seizures-being-recorded-by-i-t-dept-every-assembly-polls-cbdt-2879089%5C%22%3Esearch%20and%20seizure%20of%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20campaigns%20for%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2Fno-claimants-for-699-crore-cash-and-valuables-seized-says-chief-electoral-officer%2Farticle67566608.ece%5C%22%3Eno%20claimants%20for%20Rs%20700%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20seized%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20the%20target%20of%20the%20enforcement%20agencies%20is%20the%20opposition.%20They%20won%E2%80%99t%20dare%20touch%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Has%20Become%20an%20Excessive%20Directorate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgencies%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98laundry%20list%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20have%20a%20devious%20track%20record.%20During%20the%20Modi%20years%2C%20they%20became%20the%20chief%20instrument%20of%20repression.%20Political%20opponents%20were%20targeted%20on%20unsubstantiated%20grounds.%20Their%20raids%20have%20become%20an%20everyday%20occurrence.%20Hardly%20a%20day%20passes%20without%20the%20ED%20raiding%20or%20serving%20notices%20on%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-rules-political-leaders-not-immune-to-law-as-opposition-parties-demand-fresh-guidelines-for-arrest-remand-and-bail-politicalleaders-legalimmunity-supremecourt-oppositionparties-cbi-ed-arrest-remand-bail-guidelines-india-101680719858861.html%5C%22%3EA%20petition%20filed%20by%2014%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20highlights%20how%20Modi%20has%20ruthlessly%20misused%20the%20ED%20and%20the%20CBI%20against%20his%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ten-year%20UPA%20rule%2C%20of%20the%2026%20political%20leaders%20probed%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20only%2014%20(or%2053%25)%20were%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20petition%20said.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20victims%20shot%20up%20to%2095%25%20under%20the%20first%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20121%20political%20leaders%20investigated%2C%20115%20were%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20petition%20said%20that%20while%2060%25%20of%20political%20leaders%20the%20CBI%20investigated%20between%202004%20and%202014%20were%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20the%20number%20rose%20to%2095%25%20after%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailed%20analysis%20shows%20how%20tendentious%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20witch%20hunts%20against%20the%20opposition%20are.%20According%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20during%20the%20UPA%2C%20cases%20were