20with%20the%20BJP.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2Fmpsanjaykaka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20former%20CMs%20being%20targeted%20are%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20(a%20former%20deputy%20CM)%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Farooq%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20Nabam%20Tuki%2C%20Okram%20Ibobi%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20against%20this%2C%20the%20agencies%20have%20not%20initiated%20any%20action%20against%20BJP%20leaders%20or%20their%20allies.%20The%20moment%20a%20charge-sheeted%20opposition%20leader%20joins%20the%20BJP%2C%20all%20cases%20against%20them%20are%20withdrawn%20and%20they%20become%20a%20paragon%20of%20virtue.%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20never%20raided%20or%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20get%20sound%20sleep%20as%20there%20are%20no%20inquiries%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maharashtra%20politician%20Harshvardhan%20Patil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-wont-come-after-me-since-i-am-a-bjp-mp-sanjay-patil%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20colleague%20Sanjay%20Patil%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ED%20won%E2%80%99t%20come%20after%20me%20since%20I%20am%20a%20BJP%20MP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20many%20such%20boasts%20by%20the%20relieved%20victims%20of%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fshashi-tharoor-shares-list-politicians-graft-probe-bjp-8470853%2F%5C%22%3EShashi%20Tharoor%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98laundered%E2%80%99%20defectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20included%20such%20big%20men%20as%20Narayan%20Rane%2C%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(now%20the%20high-profile%20Assam%20CM)%2C%20Bhawana%20Gawli%2C%20Yashwant%20Jadhav%2C%20Yamini%20Jadhav%20and%20Pratap%20Sarnaik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdded%20to%20this%20was%20another%20list%20which%20included%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2F7-politicians-with-corruption-charges-cbi-and-ed-wont-raid%2F280173%2F%5C%22%3EShivraj%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20Ramesh%20Pokhriyal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20others%20like%20Mukul%20Roy%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20who%20the%20ED%20and%20CBI%20first%20targeted%20in%20a%20big%20way%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20%E2%80%98forget%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20cases%20against%20him%20when%20he%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20finally%20relaunched%20the%20cases%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20and%20CBI%20under%20Modi%20have%20been%20resorting%20to%20such%20cloak%20and%20dagger%20operations%20that%20has%20been%20part%20of%20those%20conducted%20by%20all%20hardened%20dictators%3A%20allegedly%20threatening%20people%20to%20give%20false%20statements%20to%20implicate%20victims%20in%20false%20cases%20and%20extorting%20leaders%20using%20middlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20allegations%20of%20the%20ED%20being%20used%20to%20settle%20personal%20scores.%20Punjab%20CM%20Bhagwat%20Mann%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20intimidate%20us%20by%20threatening%20arrests%20or%20sending%20ED%20summons%20%E2%80%A6%20ED%20officials%20tell%20us%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20evidence%20against%20our%20leaders%2C%20but%20they%20are%20compelled%20to%20conduct%20raids%20%E2%80%A6%20they%20have%20orders%20from%20the%20boss.%20I%20told%20them%20take%20what%20you%20find%20from%20our%20house.%20We%20will%20split%20it%2050-50.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-low-conviction-rate-caged-parrot-that-cant-get-anyone-to-sing%5C%22%3EWith%20Low%20Conviction%20Rate%2C%20ED%20Is%20Nothing%20More%20Than%20a%20Caged%20Parrot%20That%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Get%20Anyone%20to%20Sing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20the%20apparent%20temerity%20(and%2C%20allegedly%2C%20due%20authorisation)%20to%20negotiate%20defection%20deals%20with%20such%20veteran%20politicians%20as%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20speaker%20M.%20Appavu.%20The%20former%20said%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20offered%20to%20withdraw%20all%20cases%20against%20him%20provided%20he%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20speaker%20said%20for%20three%20months%2C%20he%20was%20threatened%20by%20ED%20middlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20month%2C%20Kejriwal%20came%20out%20with%20the%20revelation%20of%20an%20Operation%20Lotus%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi%20to%20lure%20away%20seven%20AAP%20MLAs.%20They%20were%20each%20offered%20Rs%2025%20crore%20and%20tickets%20for%20next%20elections%20if%20they%20defected%20to%20the%20BJP%20side%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%2C%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20were%20told%20that%20the%20ED%20will%20arrest%20him%20soon%20and%20the%20AAP%20government%20will%20be%20toppled.%20For%20his%20revealing%20this%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fthey-are-only-here-to-do-nautanki-aap-defends-arvind-kejriwal-against-notice-on-mlas-poaching-issue-416071-2024-02-03%5C%22%3Ethe%20Delhi%20police%20went%20to%20his%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20serve%20a%20notice%20to%20him%20demanding%20evidence%20for%20his%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20reportedly%20insisted%20that%20they%20hand%20over%20the%20notice%20in%20person%20to%20Kejriwal%2C%20AAP%20leaders%20present%20there%20sought%20to%20know%20under%20which%20law%20they%20were%20required%20to%20serve%20the%20notice%20directly%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20time%20ago%2C%20Shah%20had%20alleged%20that%20Meghalaya%20leader%20Conrad%20Sangma%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20corrupt%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister.%20This%20was%20before%20Sangma%20became%20a%20BJP%20ally.%20AAP%20leaders%20ask%20why%20the%20CBI%20or%20the%20police%20%E2%80%93%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20serve%20notice%20to%20Shah.%20They%20ask%3A%20Why%