-owe-rs-victory-to-your-efforts%2Farticleshow%2F59996638.cms%5C%22%3E44%20MLAs%20hosted%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%20Shivakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20multiple%20properties%20of%20Shivakumar%20were%20searched%20on%20various%20occasions%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20his%20daughter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fed-summons-dk-shivakumars-daughter%2Farticle61987298.ece%5C%22%3EAishwarya%20Shivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fed-summons-dks-wife-mother%2Farticle29684269.ece%5C%22%3Emother%20D.K.%20Gowramma%20and%20wife%20Usha%20Shivakumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20also%20issued%20summons%20by%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnational-herald-ed-again-summons-karnataka-congress-chief-d-k-shivakumar%5C%22%3Esummoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20ED%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20separate%20money%20laundering%20probe%20into%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20Congress%20party-owned%20National%20Herald%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20SC%20dismisses%20the%20longstanding%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20allowed%20the%20special%20leave%20petitions%20filed%20by%20Shivakumar%20and%20his%20aide%20Anjaneya%20Hanumanthaiah%20against%20a%202019%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20verdict%20upholding%20the%20summonses%20issued%20to%20them%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20as%20per%20the%3Cem%3E%20Live%20Law%20r%3C%2Fem%3Eeport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Shivakumar%20had%20approached%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20and%20sought%20dismissal%20of%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20ED.%20However%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20Shivakumar%20and%20others%20in%20August%202019%2C%20upholding%20the%20central%20agency%E2%80%99s%20summonses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20reason%20cited%20by%20the%20single-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20was%20that%20section%20120B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20constituted%20a%20stand-alone%20offence%20adequate%20to%20invoke%20the%20PMLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20congress%20president%20and%20his%20aide%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20apex%20court%20held%20the%20high%20court%20bench%E2%80%99s%20rationale%20as%20%E2%80%98unsustainable%E2%80%99%20in%20view%20of%20its%20recent%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-great-crossover-opposition-leaders-who-joined-the-bjp-after-action-by-central-agencies%5C%22%3EThe%20Great%20Crossover%3A%20Opposition%20Leaders%20Who%20Joined%20the%20BJP%20After%20Action%20by%20Central%20Agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20case%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20ruled%20that%20Section%20120B%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20becomes%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20%E2%80%9Conly%20when%20the%20conspiracy%20is%20directed%20towards%20committing%20an%20offence%20that%20is%20otherwise%20scheduled.%20The%20legislative%20intent%20behind%20the%20PMLA%20was%20not%20to%20make%20every%20offence%20not%20included%20in%20the%20schedule%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20by%20applying%20Section%20120B%20of%20the%20IPC%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SC%20bend%20had%20noted%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3ELive%20Law%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20a%20review%20petition%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20ED%20against%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Shivkumar%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20underlined%20that%20if%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20review%20petition%20related%20to%20the%20Pavana%20Dibbur%20judgment%20is%20accepted%2C%20then%20the%20direction%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20high%20court%20in%20the%20impugned%20judgment%20would%20stand%20affirmed%2C%20allowing%20the%20ED%20to%20seek%20a%20review%20or%20recall%20of%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20latest%20order%20if%20necessary%2C%20as%20per%20the%3Cem%3E%20Live%20La%3C%2Fem%3Ew%20report.%C2%A0%3Cb%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709640858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05163809%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-05-at-4.37.39-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-cm-dk-shivakumar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20registered%20a%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20case%20against%20Shivakumar%20in%202018%20and%20arrested%20him%20on%20September%203%2C%202019.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20granted%20him%20bail%20on%20October%2023%2C%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-dismisses-money-laundering-case-against-karnataka-deputy-cm-dk-shivakumar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%3A%20Congress%20Writes%20to%20Governor%20Over%20Controversial%20Appointment%20of%20Forest%20Official%20MK%20Yadava%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05163723%2FUntitled-design-29.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20a%20time%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20claiming%20to%20have%20been%20fighting%20corruption%2C%20Congress%20MLA%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20Assam%20assembly%2C%20Debabrata%20Saikia%2C%20has%20written%20to%20the%20state%20governor%20Gulab%20Chand%20Katari%20about%20the%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20government%E2%80%99s%20recent%20appointment%20of%20a%20recently%20retired%20controversial%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFoS)%20officer%20as%20special%20chief%20secretary%20(forest).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20M.%20K.%20Yadava%2C%20against%20whom%20there%20have%20been%20several%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20wrongdoing%20in%20Assam%2C%20had%20retired%20as%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20principal%20chief%20conservator%20(PCCF)%20this%20past%20February%2019%2C%20and%20also%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forest%20force%20(HoFF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Sarma%20government%20at%20once%20re-engaged%20him%20as%20the%20special%20chief%20secretary%20(forest)%20for%20a%20period%20of%20one%20year.%20Yadava%20is%20widely%20seen%20in%20the%20state%20as%20close%20to%20Sarma%20since%20his%20stint%20at%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-ram-nath-kovind-kaziranga-the-wire-impact%5C%22%3EAssam%20Forest%20Official%20Replaced%202%20Days%20After%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20Report%20on%20Misuse%20of%20Funds%20for%20Kovind%20Visit%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20governor%20%E2%80%93%20copies%20of%20which%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20among%20others%20%E2%80%93%20Saikia%20has%20pointed%20out%20ten%20counts%20on%20which%20Yadava%20should%20not%20have%20been%20appointed%20by%20the%20government%2C%20including%20underlining%20allegations%20of%20tampering%20with%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20while%20he%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20AEDCL-AMTRON%2C%20a%20state-owned%20company%20that%20supplies%20these%20machines%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20Sarma%20was%20then%20the%20AMTRON%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaikia%E2%80%99s%20reference%20was%20to%202009%20when%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20parties%2C%20primarily%20the%20Asom%20Gana%20Parishad%20(AGP)%2C%20now%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%2C%20had%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20EVM%20tampering%20under%20Yadava.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20as%20Special%20Chief%20Secretary%20is%20violative%20of%20Rule.%208%20of%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(Cadre)%20Rules%2C%201954%2C%20and%20the%20DoPT%E2%80%99s%20instructions%20on%20re-employing%20retired%20AIS%20and%20Central%20Services%20officers%20to%20Senior%20Duty%20Posts%2C%20on%20merits%20alone%20this%20decision%20is%20questionable%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Saikia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdopt.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRevised_AIS_Rule_Vol_II_IAS_Rule_01_0.pdf%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20following%20an%20RTI-based%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20using%20funds%20for%20tiger%20conservation%20at%20the%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20(KNP)%20by%20Yadava%E2%80%99s%20office%20to%20host%20then%20president%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%2C%20the%20Sarma%20government%20had%20issued%20a%20circular%20stating%20that%20he%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20step%20down%20from%20the%20post%20of%20the%20principal%20chief%20conservator%20of%20forests%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forest%20force.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20temporary%20measure%20as%20the%20issue%20had%20gained%20heat%20in%20the%20state%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkovind-kaziranga-crores-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Rs%2049k%20for%20Tea%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20Assam%20Govt%20Spent%20Rs%201.6%20Crores%20From%20Kaziranga%20Funds%20to%20Host%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20this%20particular%20incident%20during%20Kovind%E2%80%99s%20visit%2C%20and%20also%20that%20there%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cnumerous%20(other)%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20against%20Yadava%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20misusing%20and%20abusing%20his%20power%20and%20using%20his%20position%20to%20support%20dubious%20activities%20during%20his%20service%20innings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saikia%2C%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20underlined%20that%20%E2%80%9Chis%20appointment%20has%20sent%20a%20malefic%20signal%20to%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20and%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20Cadre%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20is%20being%20resented%20by%20one%20and%20all%2C%20including%20the%20PCCF%2C%20Wildlife.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadava%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20by%20the%20Sarma%20government%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20claiming%20at%20public%20rallies%20about%20carrying%20on%20his%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.economictimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fcriticise-me-but-action-against-corruption-will-continue-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F107436937.cms%5C%22%3Edrive%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20against%20corruption%20and%20accusing%20the%20opposition%20of%20indulging%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadava%20was%20in%20the%20news%20in%20October%202022%20too%20when%20local%20activists%20had%20filed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Flaw-is-equal-for-all-complaint-against-assam-cm-sadhguru-for-night-safari-inside-kaziranga%2F1144008%2F%5C%22%3Epolice%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20chief%20minister%20Sarma%20and%20Isha%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Jagadish%20Vasudev%20known%20as%20Sadhguru%2C%20seen%20close%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20for%20having%20entered%20the%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20at%20night%20for%20a%20safari%20in%20spite%20of%20standing%20orders%20against%20it.%20Yadava%2C%20then%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20chief%20warden%20of%20forests%2C%20had%20issued%20a%20special%20order%20to%20open%20the%20park%20gates%20for%20the%20VIP%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20ten%20counts%20of%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20power%20as%20mentioned%20by%20the%20Opposition%20leader%20in%20the%20letter%20to%20the%20governor%2C%20urging%20Raj%20Bhawan%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20in%20reconsidering%20Yadava%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20by%20the%20Assam%20government%20in%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20larger%20interest%20of%20our%20people%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Shri.%20M%20K%20Yadava%20was%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20case%20of%20the%20unauthorized%20diversion%20of%2044%20hectares%20of%20reserved%20forest%20land%20to%20set%20up%20the%20Assam%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Commando%20Battalion%20in%20Hailakandi%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Act%2C%201980.%20When%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%20took%20suo-moto%20cognizance%20of%20against%20(of)%20the%20illegal%20diversion%2C%20Shri%20M.K.%20Yadava%20followed%20it%20up%20by%20filing%20a%20false%20affidavit%20before%20the%20NGT%20which%20said%20that%20the%20land%20in%20question%20shall%20be%20utilized%20solely%20for%20erecting%20tents%20for%20the%20commandos%2C%20whereas%20the%20Google%20Earth%20Imagery%20showed%20substantial%20concrete%20structures.%20In%20fact%2C%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20was%20involved%20in%20multiple%20illegal%20diversions%20of%20reserved%20forest%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20During%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20Director%2C%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%2C%20a%20record%20number%20of%2044%20rhinos%20were%20poached%20within%20a%20span%20of%2025%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20As%20PCCF%2C%20Wildlife%20and%20PCCF%20%26amp%3B%20HoFF%2C%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20was%20totally%20apathetic%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20animal%20sensors%20installed%20at%20the%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20and%20Tiger%20Reserve%20as%20per%20honouable%20NGT%E2%80%99s%20orders%20functioned%20properly.%20They%20were%20made%20functional%20only%20during%20the%20VVIP%20visits%2C%20defeating%20their%20very%20purpose.%20The%20sensor%20cameras%20placed%20at%20Kanchanjuri%20Corridor%20(Maloni)%20were%20removed%20long%20time%20ago.%20The%20absence%20of%20speed%20checks%20resulted%20in%20increased%20number%20of%20road%20accidents%20involving%20the%20wildlife%20of%20Kaziranga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20on%20September%2023%2C%202021%20(The%20World%20Rhino%20Day)%2C%20about%202%2C500%20rhino%20horns%2C%20said%20to%20be%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20stockpile%2C%20were%20destroyed%20ostentatiously%20to%20bust%20a%20myth%20that%20the%20horns%20had%20a%20miraculous%20medicinal%20value.%20But%20doubts%20were%20expressed%20by%20several%20people%20that%20it%20was%20(they%20were)%20mostly%20fake%20horns%20that%20were%20burnt%20during%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Huge%20misappropriation%20of%20funds%20from%20the%20Kaziranga%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Foundation%20and%20Corpus%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20His%20Excellency%2C%20President%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Kaziranga%20came%20to%20light%20during%20his%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20His%20involvement%20in%20rigging%20the%20Rhino%20Population%20Estimation%202022%20figures%20was%20alleged%2C%20causing%20significant%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20Central%20and%20State%20Governments%20internationally.%20Numbers%20which%20were%20not%20supported%20by%20documentary%20evidence%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Shri%20M.K.Yadava%20also%20served%20as%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Assam%20Electronics%20Development%20Corporation%20(AEDCL-AMTRON)%20for%20a%20long%20period.%20In%20fact%2C%20there%20was%20resistance%20from%20him%20whenever%20he%20was%20transferred%20out%20of%20AMTRON%20for%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20During%202009%2C%20while%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20was%20serving%20AEDCL-AMTRON%20as%20its%20managing%2C%20AMTRON%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20of%20supplying%20EVMs%20for%20the%20general%20elections.%20The%20opposition%20parties%2C%20mainly%20Asom%20Gana%20Parishad%20(AGP)%20and%20the%20Assam%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(AUDF)%2C%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20tampering%20of%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM)%20with%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%E2%80%99s%20involvement.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20present%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Sri%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Health%20Minister%20at%20that%20time%2C%20was%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20AMTRON.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20During%20the%20same%20period%2C%20financial%20irregularities%20amounting%20to%20crores%20of%20rupees%20came%20to%20light%20in%20what%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CThin%20Client%20Scam%E2%80%9D%20in%20Assam%20Secretariat.%20In%20the%20name%20of%20installing%20LAN%2C%20Servers%20and%20Thin%20Clients%20in%20Assam%20Secretariat%2C%20huge%20amounts%20were%20allegedly%20misappropriated.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20at%20least%20two%20chief%20secretaries%20had%20put%20it%20in%20writing%20regarding%20Shri%20M.K.%20Yadava%E2%80%99s%20direct%20involvement%2C%20and%20one%20of%20them%20suggested%20that%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20should%20be%20dismissed%20from%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Further%2C%20during%20the%20incumbency%20of%20Shri.%20M.K.%20Yadava%20as%20managing%20director%2C%20AEDCL-%20AMTRON%2C%20the%20PSU%20was%20vested%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20conducting%20exams%20for%20government%20recruitment.%20However%2C%20on%20account%20of%20allegations%20regarding%20large-scale%20irregularities%2C%20and%20protests%20by%20the%20unemployed%20youth%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Assam%20had%20to%20eventually%20hand%20over%20the%20responsibility%20to%20the%20Dibrugarh%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709639093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05163723%2FUntitled-design-29.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-congress-writes-to-governor-over-controversial-appointment-of-forest-official-mk-yadava%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seen%20as%20loyalist%20of%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20retired%20forest%20service%20officer%20Yadava%20has%20been%20re-appointed%20as%20special%20chief%20secretary%20(forest).%20Congress%20leader%20Debabrata%20Saikia%20wrote%20to%20governor%20listing%20out%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Yadava.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fassam-congress-writes-to-governor-over-controversial-appointment-of-forest-official-mk-yadava%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22France%20Becomes%20the%20First%20Country%20to%20Make%20Abortion%20a%20Constitutional%20Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05165119%2Fimage-1907.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20session%20of%20parliament%20at%20the%20Palace%20of%20Versailles%20ended%20on%20Monday%20with%20the%20lawmakers%20endorsing%20the%20Bill%20to%20anchor%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fabortion%2Ft-65840883%5C%22%3Ewoman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20abortion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20French%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20make%20France%20the%20first%20country%20to%20explicitly%C2%A0protect%20the%20right%20to%20terminate%20a%20pregnancy%20in%20its%20basic%20legal%20articles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhilst%20the%20right%20to%20an%20abortion%20is%20implicit%20in%20the%20constitution%20of%20other%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20Slovenia%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20former%20Yugoslavia%20for%20example%2C%20states%20that%20everyone%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20decide%E2%80%9D%20whether%20to%20bear%20children%20%E2%80%93%20France%20is%20the%20only%20country%20to%20take%20it%20further%20and%20explicitly%20guarantee%20that%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20change%20is%20being%20made%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrance-macron-promises-to-make-abortion-rights-irreversible%2Fa-67249137%5C%22%3Epromised%20the%20measure%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%202022%20rolling%20back%20of%20abortion%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Elysee%20Palace%20has%20proposed%20that%20Article%2034%20of%20the%20French%20constitution%20be%C2%A0amended%20to%20specify%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20law%20determines%20the%20conditions%20by%20which%20is%20exercised%20the%20freedom%20of%20women%20to%20have%20recourse%20to%20an%20abortion%2C%20which%20is%20guaranteed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMacron%E2%80%99s%20government%20aims%C2%A0to%20make%20%E2%80%9Ca%20woman%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20have%20an%20abortion%20irreversible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20vote%2C%20Macron%20said%20France%20was%20sending%20a%20%E2%80%9Cuniversal%20message%E2%80%9D%20by%20defending%20abortion%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20this%20happening%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Assembly%2C%20France%E2%80%99s%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament%2C%20overwhelmingly%20approved%20making%20abortion%20a%20%E2%80%9Cguaranteed%20freedom%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20constitution.%20The%20country%E2%80%99s%20upper%20house%2C%20the%20Senate%2C%20did%20the%20same%20last%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20congress%20of%20both%20houses%20met%20at%C2%A0Versailles%2C%20where%20the%20lawmakers%20eventually%20gave%20it%20the%20three-fifths%20supermajority%20needed%20for%20a%20constitutional%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20want%20to%20attack%20the%20freedoms%20of%20a%20people%2C%20we%20always%20start%20with%20that%20of%20women%2C%E2%80%9D%20French%20Prime%20Minister%20Gabriel%20Attal%20told%20those%20gathered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20freedoms%20are%20inherently%20threatened.%20Inherently%20fragile%2C%20in%20essence%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20those%20who%20decide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20had%20faced%20initial%20resistance%20in%20the%20right-leaning%20Senate.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20represented%20in%20parliament%20has%20questioned%20the%20right%20to%20abortion%2C%20which%20France%20decriminalised%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVatican%2C%20French%20bishops%20oppose%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fabortion-us-marks-a-year-since-roe-v-wade-reversal%2Fa-66013358%5C%22%3Ereverse%20the%20%3Cem%3ERoe%20v.%20Wade%3C%2Fem%3E%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20recognised%20women%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20right%20to%20abortion%2C%20prompted%20activists%20to%20press%20for%20France%20to%20make%20the%20constitutional%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20this%20event%20is%20not%20isolated%3A%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20even%20in%20Europe%2C%20there%20are%20currents%20of%20opinion%20that%20seek%20to%20hinder%20at%20any%20cost%20the%20freedom%20of%20women%20to%20terminate%20their%20pregnancy%20if%20they%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20introduction%20to%20the%20bill%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vatican%20on%20Monday%20repeated%20its%20opposition%20to%20the%20change%2C%20echoing%20concerns%20already%20raised%20by%20French%20Catholic%20bishops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Pontifical%20Academy%20for%20Life%20recalls%20that%20in%20the%20era%20of%20universal%20human%20rights%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20%E2%80%98right%E2%80%99%20to%20take%20a%20human%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Vatican%20institution%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrance-makes-abortion-a-constitutional-right%2Fa-68434557%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20DW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709637905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F05165119%2Fimage-1907.png%2