y%20remembers%20the%20time%20he%20took%20his%20first%20photograph%20in%20the%20wild%20back%20in%20April%202019.%C2%A0%3Cem%3E(Image%20above%20of%20Karamjeet%3B%20Snow%20Leopard)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20photo%20that%20I%20took%20in%20the%20wild%20after%20I%20got%20my%20first%20camera%20was%20of%20a%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20in%20a%20village%20called%20Huliya%20near%20Drass.%20The%20photo%20was%20of%20a%20mother%20and%20her%20cub%20playing%20in%20the%20snow.%20Witnessing%20these%20majestic%20creatures%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%20was%20a%20very%20captivating%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20to%20document%20that%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Karamjeet%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20Karamjeet%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcaramjeet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Instagram%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20spell-binding%20photographs%20of%20the%20wildlife%20in%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%20In%20his%20photos%2C%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20capture%20a%20variety%20of%20endangered%20species%20ranging%20from%20the%20elusive%20snow%20leopard%20(%3Cem%3EPanthera%20uncia%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20the%20solitary%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20(%3Cem%3EUrsus%20arctos%20isabellinus%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Pallas%E2%80%99s%20Cat%20(%3Cem%3EOtocolobus%20manul%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Tibetan%20Wolf%20(%3Cem%3ECanis%20lupus%20chanco%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20the%20Urial%20(%3Cem%3EOvis%20orientalis)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Eurasian%20eagle%20owl%20(%3Cem%3EBubo%20bubo%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20bearded%20vulture%20(%3Cem%3EGypaetus%20barbatus)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20beyond%20wildlife%2C%20Karamjeet%20has%20also%20captured%20spectacular%20photos%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20its%20tribes%20and%20night%20skies.%20As%20Karamjeet%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLadakh%20contains%20an%20amazing%20range%20of%20wildlife%2C%20including%20birds%20and%20mammals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20shame%20not%20many%20people%20notice%20these%20incredible%20creatures.%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20awestruck%20by%20the%20beauty%20around%20us%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20capture%20it%20with%20my%20camera.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20his%20Nikon%20D750%20with%20a%20200-500%20mm%20lens%20which%20his%20father%20got%20him%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20a%20lot%20of%20persisting%E2%80%9D%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20Karamjeet%E2%80%99s%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Mr%20Brown%20Bear%20(%40caramjeet)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELadakh%20is%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramjeet%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20established%20roots%20in%20Kargil%20for%20over%20five%20generations.%20Their%20home%20today%20lies%20in%20Balti%20Bazaar%2C%20which%20is%20situated%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271231%2Fstanzin-saldon-shifah-kargil-gender-equality-public-school-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKargil%20town%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20move%20to%20Ladakh%20was%20made%20by%20my%20great-great-grandfather%2C%20who%20migrated%20from%20Mirpur%20(now%20in%20Pakistan)%20for%20trade.%20He%20settled%20in%20Kargil%20after%20marrying%20a%20woman%20hailing%20from%20a%20Buddhist%20family%20in%20Shargole%2C%20Kargil.%20In%20our%20small%20and%20tight-knit%20Sikh%20community%20in%20Kargil%2C%20familial%20ties%20are%20strong.%20There%20are%20barely%2050%20of%20us%20but%20we%20are%20engaged%20in%20various%20occupations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14631369.2023.2236040%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520rural%2520population%2520in%2520Kargil%2Caround%2520360%2520Sikhs%252C%2520in%2520town.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Malvika%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20in%20%E2%80%98Partition%2C%20identity%20and%20belonging%20among%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20borderland%20district%20of%20Kargil%2C%20Ladakh%E2%80%99%2C%20for%20Asian%20Ethnicity%2C%20%E2%80%9CSikhs%20in%20Ladakh%20arrived%20as%20traders%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20settled%20around%20the%20major%20trading%20centres%20along%20the%20silk-route%20such%20as%20Skardu%2C%20Kargil%2C%20Leh%20in%20the%20then%20undivided%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%20as%20it%20existed%20before%201947-partition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20members%20of%20his%20family%20who%20established%20their%20business%20ventures%2C%20his%20father%20pursued%20a%20career%20as%20a%20government%20school%20teacher.%20While%20one%20of%20his%20uncles%20is%20also%20a%20school%20teacher%2C%20the%20others%20are%20proprietors%20of%20tea-selling%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaramjeet%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20developed%20his%20love%20for%20photography%20at%20a%20local%20photo%20studio%20in%20Kargil%20while%20he%20was%20still%20studying%20at%20the%20Suru%20Valley%20Public%20School.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20developed%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322499%2Fnaval-officer-captain-navtej-singh-captures-life-at-sea-in-india-in-stunning-photos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephotography%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20spending%20time%20at%20a%20local%20shop%20called%20Canon%20Photographer%2C%20where%20I%20often%20observed%20Anoop%20Singh%2C%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Sanjeet%20Singh%2C%20passionately%20capturing%20and%20editing%20photos.%20This%20experience%20ignited%20my%20fascination%20for%20photography%2C%20leading%20me%20to%20pursue%20a%20Bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20journalism%20and%20mass%20communication%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20graduating%20from%20journalism%20school%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Kargil%20Today%2C%20a%20local%20media%20channel%2C%20where%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20photographer%20and%20media%20professional%20for%20over%20three%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3-jOR6xPBL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F